    <title>摺疊（Collapse） &amp; 手風琴（Accordion）元件製作</title>
    <url>/payroom-frontend-blog/2024/08/21/%E6%91%BA%E7%96%8A-%E6%89%8B%E9%A2%A8%E7%90%B4%E5%85%83%E4%BB%B6%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="摺疊"><a href="#摺疊" class="headerlink" title="摺疊"></a>摺疊</h2><h3 id="基本-HTML-CSS"><a href="#基本-HTML-CSS" class="headerlink" title="基本 HTML + CSS"></a>基本 HTML + CSS</h3><p>想要實現最單純的折疊的話，其實使用原生的 HTML 標籤就可以辦到。<br>那麼該如何實現呢？答案就是 <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> + <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code>，</p>
<p>MDN: <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details">details</a> <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary">summary</a></p>
<p> <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 是外層標籤，會包覆 <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> 與 其他內容。<br><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> 就是顯示在外面的標題，其他的內容會被隱藏。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span>原生<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>這是你的內容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>這些都會被隱藏<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> 就是顯示在外面的標題，其他的內容會被隱藏。<br>這樣畫面上可以出現一個可以摺疊的選單了！！</p>
<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724187385/collapse-1.gif" alt="原生collapse"></p>
<h4 id="預設展開"><a href="#預設展開" class="headerlink" title="預設展開"></a>預設展開</h4><p>當展開時  <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 會變成 <code>&lt;details open&gt;</code>，所以想預設展開則使用  <code>&lt;details open&gt;</code> 。</p>
<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724187027/collapse-2.gif" alt="open屬性"></p>
<h4 id="Marker-修改"><a href="#Marker-修改" class="headerlink" title="Marker 修改"></a>Marker 修改</h4><p>如果想要修改 <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> 前面的 Marker 有兩種方法 ：</p>
<p>1.偽元素 <code>::marker</code></p>
<figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span><span class="selector-class">.marker</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-tag">summary</span><span class="selector-pseudo">::marker</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">20px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: red;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">content</span>: <span class="string">&quot;↑&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &amp;<span class="selector-attr">[open]</span> &gt; <span class="selector-tag">summary</span><span class="selector-pseudo">::marker</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">content</span>: <span class="string">&quot;↓&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>2.list-style-type</p>
<figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span><span class="selector-class">.marker-list</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-tag">summary</span><span class="selector-pseudo">::marker</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">20px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: blue;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-tag">summary</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">list-style-type</span>: <span class="string">&quot;⬇&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &amp;<span class="selector-attr">[open]</span> &gt; <span class="selector-tag">summary</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">list-style-type</span>: <span class="string">&quot;⬆ &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724222324/collapse-3.gif" alt="marker"></p>
<p>我們可以修改一點 CSS，讓其看起來比較好理解。</p>
<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724224278/collapse-4.gif" alt="clear"></p>
<h4 id="展開動畫"><a href="#展開動畫" class="headerlink" title="展開動畫"></a>展開動畫</h4><p>要加上展開動畫，以筆者目前已知的方法幾種</p>
<ol>
<li>max-height<br>常見使用的方式應該是 <code>max-height</code> ，藉由控制 <code>details</code> 的 <code>max-height</code> 來達到向下展開的效果。</li>
</ol>
<p>HTML：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span>標題<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>CSS：</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">600px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">outline</span>: <span class="number">1px</span> solid blue;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: grey;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-height</span>:<span class="number">22px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">transition</span>: max-height <span class="number">3s</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.content</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">200px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span><span class="selector-attr">[open]</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-height</span>:<span class="number">500px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果如下(先不加上 <code>overflow:hidden</code> )：</p>
<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724253438/collapse-5.gif" alt="max-height"></p>
<p>原理是控制 <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 的 max-height 來顯示內容，當<code>&lt;details&gt;</code>內有 <code>open</code>時除了<code>&lt;summary&gt;</code>以外的內容都會顯示。<br>如上圖所示 <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> 出現之後 <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 的高度才會慢慢跟上 ，如果加上 <code>overflow:hidden</code> 就會比較完整。</p>
<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724254007/collapse-6.gif" alt="max-height-overflow-hidden"></p>
<p>但是！新的問題出現了，就是關閉時會瞬間消失，沒辦法像打開時一樣緩緩向上收合，解法也有幾種：</p>
<h5 id="max-height"><a href="#max-height" class="headerlink" title="max-height"></a>max-height</h5><ul>
<li><p>input:check + max-hight<br>簡單來說，就是讓 checkbox 去控制收合( max-height )。<code>&lt;input&gt;</code> 要放在 <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 的裡面或是外面都可以。</p>
  <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;checkbox&quot;</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;details&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span> <span class="attr">open</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span> <span class="attr">for</span>=<span class="string">&quot;details&quot;</span>&gt;</span>標題<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!--  &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;details&quot; /&gt; 放這裡也可以   --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

  <figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">600px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-height</span>:<span class="number">21px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">overflow</span>:hidden;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: lightblue;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">transition</span>: max-height <span class="number">1s</span> ease-in-out;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">summary</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: block;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">label</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: block;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">cursor</span>:pointer;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">input</span><span class="selector-attr">[type=checkbox]</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>:none;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">input</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:checked</span> + <span class="selector-tag">details</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-height</span>: <span class="number">800px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 如果 input 放在裡面  details:has( input:checked )*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724309685/collapse-7.gif" alt="collapse + input::checked"></p>
<p><a href="https://dev.to/jgustavoas/how-to-fully-animate-the-details-html-element-with-only-css-no-javascript-2n88">參考資料</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<ul>
<li><p>把內容放在外層 + max-height</p>
<p>其實跟 checkbox 差不多，都是藉由 <code>detail[open]</code> 去改變 <code>max-height</code>。</p>
  <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;details-container&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      標題</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

  <figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">600px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: lightblue;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.content</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: lightgrey;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">600px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-height</span>: <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">overflow</span>: hidden;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">transition</span>: max-height <span class="number">2s</span> ease-in-out;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span><span class="selector-attr">[open]</span> + <span class="selector-class">.content</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-height</span>: <span class="number">500px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>參考資料 : <a href="https://medium.com/@jgustavo.wd/solved-how-to-fully-animate-the-details-html-element-with-only-css-no-javascript-b7d32c53a9d7">文章連結</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h5 id="grid-template-rows"><a href="#grid-template-rows" class="headerlink" title="grid-template-rows"></a>grid-template-rows</h5><p>結構跟 <code>max-height</code> 差不多，也可以做出相同的效果，但結構上就得使用 <code>&lt;details&gt; + 內容</code>。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      標題</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;details-content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">600px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: lightblue;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.details-content</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: lightcyan;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: grid;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">grid-template-rows</span>: <span class="number">0</span>fr;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">transition</span>: grid-template-rows <span class="number">500ms</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 隱藏內容 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.details-content</span> &gt; * &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">overflow</span>: hidden;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span><span class="selector-attr">[open]</span> + <span class="selector-class">.details-content</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">grid-template-rows</span>: <span class="number">1</span>fr;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>但這邊要注意的是， <code>.details-content</code> 與下一層的元素都不能加 margin or padding ，否則就會造成畫面有多餘的空白，如下圖：</p>
<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724386661/collapse-8.png" alt="extra blank"></p>
<p>目前筆者能想到的辦法就是再多寫一層，把內容多包一層</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    標題 1</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 不是這層  --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;inner-content&quot;</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 要在這層才正確  --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724397545/collapse-9.gif" alt="grid-template-rows-custom-style"></p>
<hr>
<h3 id="使用框架"><a href="#使用框架" class="headerlink" title="使用框架"></a>使用框架</h3><p>如果不想手刻，用熱門的 UI框架也是很好的選擇，不過筆者當初就是想練習自己動手試試看，能不能自己弄一個出來，所以才寫下此篇文章。</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.2/components/collapse/">BootStrap5</a></li>
<li><a href="https://element-plus.org/zh-CN/component/collapse.html#collapse-%E6%8A%98%E5%8F%A0%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF">Element Plus</a></li>
<li><a href="https://vuetifyjs.com/zh-Hans/components/expansion-panels/#section-4f7f7528">Vuetify</a></li>
<li><a href="https://daisyui.com/components/collapse/">daisyUI</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="手風琴"><a href="#手風琴" class="headerlink" title="手風琴"></a>手風琴</h2><h3 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title="&lt;details&gt;"></a><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></h3><p>在多個  <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 加上屬性 <code>&lt;name=&quot;自訂名稱&quot;&gt;</code>，每個 <code>name</code> 的屬性值相同，會被視作同一組，只要其中一個 <code>open</code> ，原本 <code>open</code> 的  <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 就會移除 <code>open</code> 屬性。<br>讓我們沿用上面的 <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 來做示範</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;accordion&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    標題 1</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;accordion&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    標題 2</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;inner-content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>這是標題 2 內容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果如下：<br><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724417679/accordion-1.gif" alt="accordion"></p>
<h3 id="使用框架-Accordion"><a href="#使用框架-Accordion" class="headerlink" title="使用框架-Accordion"></a>使用框架-Accordion</h3><p>當然…許多主流的框架也有相同的原件。</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.2/components/accordion/">BootStrap5</a></li>
<li><a href="https://element-plus.org/zh-CN/component/collapse.html#collapse-%E6%8A%98%E5%8F%A0%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF">Element Plus</a></li>
<li><a href="https://vuetifyjs.com/zh-Hans/components/expansion-panels/#section-4f7f7528">Vuetify</a></li>
<li><a href="https://daisyui.com/components/accordion/">daisyUI</a></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="小結"><a href="#小結" class="headerlink" title="小結"></a>小結</h2><p>目前會遇到的問題是內容的收合，原因是 <code>height: auto</code> 在展開時不能套用 <code>transition</code>，所以無法實現向下緩慢展開，筆者已知實現動畫收合的方法有兩種，但這兩種方法都各有缺點：</p>
<ol>
<li>max-height，當 height &gt; max-height 時，內容會變得不完整。</li>
<li>grid-template-rows，如果想要調整內容的 CSS ，HTML 結構會變得複雜。</li>
</ol>
<p><code>max-height</code> 的缺點示範，應該要能看到 5 ，但只能看到 3：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    標題 1</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">summary</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">details</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>4<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>5<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.content</span> <span class="selector-tag">li</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">padding-block</span>: <span class="number">20px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">details</span><span class="selector-attr">[open]</span> + <span class="selector-class">.content</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-height</span>:<span class="number">200px</span>; </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dofhdwmow/image/upload/v1724399680/collapse-10.gif" alt="max-height"></p>
<p>解決的方法很簡單，把 <code>max-height</code> 設定得夠大就可以。例如：<code>max-height: 2000px;</code> 。</p>
<p>總而言之，筆者覺得 <code>details[open] + .content</code> + <code>max-height</code> 用起來比較順手，老實說如果不在乎美觀與動畫效果的話，原生的 <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 就很夠用了。</p>
<p>如果需要的是手風琴(Accordion)效果， <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> + <code>name</code> 這個方法就已經很夠用了。</p>
<p>筆者在上網查詢時，發現 <code>calc-size</code> 與 偽元素 <code>::details-content</code>這兩個酷東西，如果能套用<code>height:calc-size(auto)</code> 似乎就能直接實現動畫收合，而 <code>::details-content</code> 則可以定義 <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> 內容樣式，但很可惜目前還尚未支援。</p>
<p>文章連結：<a href="https://blog.webdevsimplified.com/2024-07/css-calc-size/">calc-size</a>   <a href="https://css-tricks.com/almanac/selectors/d/details-content/">::details-content</a></p>
